{"tid":2314842,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"現在有一場大型分化行動進行中","createTime":"2020-12-06T20:46:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-07T00:30:28.000Z","uid":205928,"like":4,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f84edb7b2022fc6fc13287766bbd09280857150a","tid":2314842,"uid":205928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T20:46:12.000Z","msg":"地點就係娛台入面<br />\n有心人士企圖將日本成員同韓國成員分化<br />\n利用今次既IZONE CB<br />\n對家刻意用言論將雙金塑造成<br />\n無腦做C位，究極空降閪+蝦日本妹<br />\n加上依家有言論指<br />\n如果將來永續就會民意逆轉<br />\n我明白和理非WIZONE嘅顧慮<br />\n但希望大家尊重前線公司決定<br />\n我哋唔係黑警，五毛一樣可以隨便踩人哋偶像嘅人<br />\n<br />\n另外我呼籲勇武wizone語氣唔好咁重<br />\n一上黎就直接屌鳩娛台五毛老母<br />\n大家都係手足，可以互相溝通<br />\n亦都唔好講到之前嘅所有行動<br />\n都係WIZONE嘅功勞<br />\n因為從來一場成功嘅社運，和理非與勇武缺一不可"},{"pid":"2e05b860997608cd1f3e14a7d0f6e88e9e0dbac5","tid":2314842,"uid":152123,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T20:46:57.000Z","msg":"夜喇 瞓啦"},{"pid":"ee2853e6bfa4a2756eb88e741388837e07b764b6","tid":2314842,"uid":205928,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"2e05b860997608cd1f3e14a7d0f6e88e9e0dbac5","tid":2314842,"uid":152123,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T20:46:57.000Z","msg":"夜喇 瞓啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T20:47:17.000Z","msg":"岩岩醒📸📸"},{"pid":"112990b974961c95fc9f17fbd966bf2b2b322060","tid":2314842,"uid":205928,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T20:48:25.000Z","msg":"[KPOP] K-pop 2020討論區(36)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/rCbyqMX\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/rCbyqMX</a><br />\n#653 回覆 - 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n以上五毛狗 mark低左"},{"pid":"ade7434aa5ae8ba1a31dc43d82f5425f3fbfb7b9","tid":2314842,"uid":205928,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T21:08:05.000Z","msg":"嚴防分化！！！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xKrd65z.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxKrd65z.png&h=bff63fd6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"db1d09c775cd37afa1c5673c25e7cfb71a67e0cc